OL,7,FThe report was authored by the IIEA's
OL,8,FJohn FitzGerald of Trinity College
OL,9,FDublin and Prof Edgar Morgenroth of
OL,10,FDublin City University.
OL,12,FThe report said the cost to the
OL,13,FBritish Government of running Northern
OL,14,FIreland amounts to 12.3 billion euro a
OL,15,Fyear.
OL,17,FThe costs are based on pre-pandemic
OL,18,F2019 figures.
