OL,7,FThe report stated that the
OL,8,Funifications costs minus the UK
OL,9,Ftreasury subvention would run to
OL,10,Faround 11 billion euro.
OL,12,FBut this figure would rise to 20
OL,13,Fbillion euro when others factors,
OL,14,Fincluding social welfare and public
OL,15,Fservice pay, are included.
OL,17,FThis would require an increase in
OL,18,Ftaxation and a significant reduction
OL,19,Fin public expenditure.
