OL,7,FSinn Fein whip Padraig Mac Lochlainn
OL,8,Fsaid that he disputed the methodology
OL,9,Fused in the report.
OL,11,FThe Donegal TD claimed that the
OL,12,Fanalysis was static.
OL,14,F"You are accepting the amount of
OL,15,Fsubvention on face value," he added.
OL,17,F"Prof John Doyle of DCU in recent
OL,18,Ftimes has written that the actual
OL,19,Fsubvention is much less.
OL,21,F"It's about 2.4 billion.
