OL,7,F"That's a quarter when you deduct the
OL,8,Fpensions, debt repayments,
OL,9,Fcontribution to the defence forces of
OL,10,FBritain and so on.
OL,12,F"It's much less than the headline
OL,13,Ffigure.
OL,15,F"But also the report assumes there
OL,16,Fwill be no economic growth in the
OL,17,Fnorth.
OL,19,F"We know that since Brexit there has
OL,20,Fbeen substantial growth in the all-
OL,21,FIreland economy.
